<db:section xml:id="containsMouse-prop">
<db:title>[read-only] containsMouse : const bool</db:title>
<db:para>Holds <db:code>true</db:code> if the <db:link xlink:href="qt3dinput-qmousehandler.xml">QMouseHandler</db:link> currently contains the mouse.</db:para>
<db:note>
<db:para>In this context, contains mean that the ray originating from the mouse is intersecting with the <db:link xlink:href="qt3dcore-qentity.xml">Qt3DCore::QEntity</db:link> that aggregates the current <db:link xlink:href="qt3dinput-qmousehandler.xml">QMouseHandler</db:link> instance component.</db:para>
</db:note>
<db:para>
<db:emphasis role="bold">Access functions:
</db:emphasis>
</db:para>
<db:itemizedlist>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:type>bool</db:type> <db:emphasis role="bold">containsMouse</db:emphasis>() const</db:para>
</db:listitem>
</db:itemizedlist>
<db:para>
